Anyway, flat's yours if you want it.
I'd change the sheets if I were you.

17:26.240 --> 17:27.120
See ya.

17:27.200 --> 17:28.040
Cheers, Ken.

17:41.200 --> 17:42.720
-Hello.
-Hiya.

17:45.000 --> 17:45.840
Tonic.

17:47.800 --> 17:48.640
And a lemon.

17:48.720 --> 17:49.600
Cheers.

17:51.960 --> 17:54.000
-How's it going?
-Yeah, all right.

17:56.880 --> 17:58.360
Hello, pretty.

17:58.920 --> 18:00.960
Pretty. Hello, pretty girl.

18:01.040 --> 18:04.480
Hello. Yes, yes, yes, yes.
Where's the kisses? Who's a good girl?

18:14.200 --> 18:15.040
<i>What?</i>

18:15.120 --> 18:18.480
-<i>Nothing. Don't forget the lemon.</i>
<i>-I won't forget the lemon.</i>

18:24.640 --> 18:26.360
<i>-Who's that?</i>
-<i>Lionel.</i>

18:26.440 --> 18:29.560
<i>Right. Lionel. I can't cut him now, can I?</i>

18:29.640 --> 18:30.880
<i>Or throw him away.</i>

18:31.600 --> 18:32.440
<i>Stop!</i>

18:32.960 --> 18:35.320
<i>Stop drawing faces on the fruit and veg!</i>

18:46.560 --> 18:48.520
I've done you a gin and tonic.

18:48.600 --> 18:52.120
I don't know what you want to do
with the lemon. I'll get you some ice.

18:52.200 --> 18:53.040
Okay.

18:55.040 --> 18:57.520
-You've drawn a face on it?
-That's Lionel.

19:01.600 --> 19:02.440
Dead.

19:07.400 --> 19:09.800
-Are you getting the ice?
-Yeah.

19:15.160 --> 19:17.560
-Only me.
-Bloody hell, Ken. Do you not knock?

19:17.640 --> 19:20.600
Don't worry about that.
You got nothing I want to see. Trust me.

19:20.680 --> 19:24.320
No, I'm gonna be popping in all the time.
Don't you worry. We'll be besties.

19:25.520 --> 19:29.000
I get ever so bored in the office.
There's nothing at all coming in for him.

19:29.080 --> 19:31.760
Oh, the stories I could tell you
about this place.

19:31.840 --> 19:36.240
Absolutely dripping with memories.
Literally dripping. Throw that towel away.

19:36.320 --> 19:38.400
Anyway, I'll let you get on. Ta-ra.

19:45.360 --> 19:46.840
-All right, Brian?
-Mustn't grumble.

19:46.920 --> 19:48.040
Here to see James?

19:48.120 --> 19:50.600
-Where is the little bugger?
-He's in the bath, but come in.

19:50.680 --> 19:51.560
Oy.

19:58.120 --> 19:59.920
-What?
-All right, boy?

20:00.000 --> 20:01.320
-Mum?
-What, love?

20:02.080 --> 20:03.840
-I'm having a bath.
-Good boy.

20:03.920 --> 20:05.480
Bloody steamy in here, innit?

20:05.560 --> 20:09.120
Yeah. Told him he has it too hot.
Bad for his testicles.

20:09.200 --> 20:10.280
Makes you sterile.

20:10.360 --> 20:11.880
Ah. Do you mind?

20:12.840 --> 20:14.360
Yeah, they do look red, mate.

20:16.240 --> 20:18.800
Oh, yeah. Put a bit of cold
on them, James.

20:18.880 --> 20:22.040
Can we stop talking
about my bloody testicles? They're fine.

20:22.120 --> 20:23.560
Some cake, Brian?

20:23.640 --> 20:25.440
-Oh, yes, please. Thank you.
-James?

20:25.520 --> 20:28.520
-I'm having a fucking bath!
-Is that a yes or a no?

20:28.600 --> 20:29.560
What kind of cake?

20:30.240 --> 20:33.120
Chocolate gateau
with crumbled Flakes on top.

20:33.200 --> 20:34.040
Mm.

20:34.120 --> 20:36.080
Yes, then, please.

20:39.280 --> 20:40.640
I've gotta get my own place.

20:41.280 --> 20:43.160
-Why?
-Why?

20:43.880 --> 20:47.320
Living the dream, mate. Wish I had a woman
bringing me cake in the bath.

20:47.400 --> 20:48.920
Not your mum though.

20:49.640 --> 20:52.280
I'm not needed here anymore.
Mum's got Lenny.

20:52.840 --> 20:55.280
I'm just a big, fat lump taking up space.

20:56.280 --> 20:59.920
And your mum shouldn't be telling you off
for ruining your testicles in the bath.

21:00.000 --> 21:04.440
-You can move in with me if you want.
-Really? Do you have a spare room?

21:04.520 --> 21:08.280
-Yeah, if you can get in there.
-What do you mean <i>if </i>I can get in it?

21:08.360 --> 21:09.440
It's full of shit.

21:10.000 --> 21:11.040
You know what?

21:12.640 --> 21:13.480
Let's do it.

21:14.520 --> 21:16.120
Time for me to become a man.

21:17.600 --> 21:19.680
Will you help me break the news to my mum?

21:20.440 --> 21:21.280
Hmm.

21:27.560 --> 21:28.400
Let's see.

21:29.040 --> 21:29.880
Interesting.

21:29.960 --> 21:30.920
What?

21:31.000 --> 21:34.520
Strong, confident, determined

21:35.760 --> 21:37.080
on the outside.

21:39.400 --> 21:41.840
But on the inside,
you're vulnerable and sensitive.

21:44.880 --> 21:45.840
You're lonely.

21:47.960 --> 21:50.960
It's tough, isn't it?
Being a strong woman in a man's world.

21:52.080 --> 21:53.720
You feel you've lost a little of yourself,

21:53.800 --> 21:56.920
and you see needing comfort
as a weakness they'll pounce on.

21:58.000 --> 21:59.440
So you deny you need it.

22:01.120 --> 22:02.600
But you do need it, dear.

22:03.600 --> 22:04.800
Everyone does.

22:28.560 --> 22:29.440
-Mum.
-Yeah?

22:30.320 --> 22:33.680
-I've got something to tell you.
-Oh, I've known for ages, darling.

22:34.280 --> 22:35.120
What?

22:35.640 --> 22:37.720
Oh, sorry, what were you gonna say?

22:38.640 --> 22:41.960
Okay, um, so I think it's time
for me to fly the nest.

22:42.560 --> 22:45.200
Brian's got a spare room.
I'm gonna move in with him.

22:45.280 --> 22:48.080
Okay. Well, I'll help you
move in tomorrow, then.

22:48.960 --> 22:50.440
-Tomorrow?
-Yeah.

22:54.600 --> 22:55.880
Great.

22:58.960 --> 23:01.880
I will go and get dressed, then.

23:01.960 --> 23:02.880
Yeah.

23:06.400 --> 23:07.640
-Aw.
-I know.

23:08.600 --> 23:10.600
I'll put a snooker table in his room.

23:11.160 --> 23:13.640
-It won't fit, will it?
-Just a little one.

23:18.440 --> 23:19.680
You've got the lock on!

23:20.200 --> 23:21.560
Yeah, I'm in bed.

23:22.280 --> 23:23.160
It's Ken.

23:24.040 --> 23:25.520
Yeah, I guessed that.

23:26.200 --> 23:30.680
I've had an idea for a new showbiz
gossip piece called <i>Careless Whispers</i>.

23:31.680 --> 23:33.120
Okay. Tell me tomorrow.

23:33.200 --> 23:36.200
Yeah, it's basically
a list of all the people I know

23:36.280 --> 23:38.760
who claim they've
wanked off George Michael.

23:38.840 --> 23:40.760
Okay. I'm going to sleep.

23:40.840 --> 23:42.480
-Good idea though, isn't it?
-Yeah.

23:42.560 --> 23:43.640
Yeah. Night night.

23:43.720 --> 23:45.280
-Yeah, night, Ken!
-What?

23:45.360 --> 23:47.360
-Night, Ken!
-Yeah, all right.

23:50.720 --> 23:51.920
See you tomorrow.

23:52.000 --> 23:53.120
-See ya.
-See you.

23:53.720 --> 23:55.120
-Don't bother getting up.
-Hmm.

23:55.200 --> 23:56.200
Hmm.

23:56.280 --> 23:57.240
-Cheers.
-Bye.

23:57.320 --> 23:58.160
Bye.

