-<i>Is that a new toy?</i>

24:42.680 --> 24:44.840
<i>I'm doing your accounts!</i>

24:44.920 --> 24:46.920
<i>I would never get bored with this.</i>

24:47.640 --> 24:48.880
<i>Unless I was working.</i>

24:49.440 --> 24:50.840
<i>-Yeah.</i>
-<i>Then it'd be annoying.</i>

24:50.920 --> 24:53.440
<i>-Yeah. It is annoying.</i>

24:53.520 --> 24:56.400
<i>-Can you take the squeaker out?</i>
-<i>No, look at her.</i>

24:59.920 --> 25:00.760
Hello.

25:05.120 --> 25:07.880
<i>-Squeak it.</i>

25:07.960 --> 25:09.480
<i>Squeak it.</i>

25:09.560 --> 25:12.600
<i>-Oh! </i>

25:25.560 --> 25:29.600
<i>Lullabies? ♪</i>

25:35.840 --> 25:36.680
Bedtime.
